body:
Didn`t you want to have an OP weapon? With that mod, you can get one. Karambit - OP weapon that deals 20 damage to any entity. Craft Platinum, craft Metal, and get your own Karambit. If you see some bugs or issues, tell me in the comments.

For getting one Karambit you need:
   16 iron ingots;
   12 diamonds;
   24 gold;
   1 black wool;


For crafting Platinum, you need to get 4 gold and 1 diamond

For getting Metal, you need to get 1 Platinum, 4 iron ingots, 2 diamonds and 2 gold

With 4 Metal and 1 blackwool you can make just one karambit.

**_REMEMBER! There is a bug on some versions where Karambits can stack up to 64 instead of 1._**

**_Also new versions may not be visible in modrinth app!_**
